<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <a class="logo" href="/">LessonAI</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/signin">Sign In</a>
      <a class="button" href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="hero">
    <section class="hero-text">
      <h1>Create classroom lesson plans in seconds.</h1>
      <p>LessonAI helps teachers generate lesson plans with objectives, activities, assessments, and exit tickets.</p>
      <div>
        <a class="button" href="/signup">Get Started</a>
        <a class="button ghost" href="/signin">I already have an account</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="preview-card">
      <h2>Lesson Plan Preview</h2>
      <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Science</p>
      <p><strong>Topic:</strong> Photosynthesis</p>
      <p><strong>Sections:</strong> Objective, Warm-Up, Practice, Assessment</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <section class="features">
    <article>
      <h3>Secure accounts</h3>
      <p>Users sign up and sign in before using the dashboard.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>AI generation</h3>
      <p>The backend sends the form details to an AI API.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>Saved history</h3>
      <p>Lesson plans are saved to MongoDB.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
